tk1665703199671.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/itk1665703199671.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/itk1665703199671.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"itk1665703199671\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Get the timer message from the UTIMER component.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"itk1665703199671__topic_d136013e1_d136014e1_d136015e1\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104itk1665703199671_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"itk1665703199671__codeblock_g42_njg_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation getMessage\nparams\n   string MsgDestination : OUT\n   string MsgId          : OUT\n   string MsgData        : OUT\nendparams</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"itk1665703199671__section_j1w_njg_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d450261e56\">Parameters</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"itk1665703199671__ul_c1g_pjg_hwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"itk1665703199671__li_d48215e1_d48216e1_d48217e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">MsgDestination</var>—path to the\n               component instance to which the message is sent.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"itk1665703199671__li_d48218e1_d48219e1_d48220e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">MsgId</var>—message ID of the\n               message that is sent to the component.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"itk1665703199671__li_d48221e1_d48222e1_d48223e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">MsgData</var>—message data that is\n               sent to the component.</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"itk1665703199671__section_rlg_qjg_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d450261e80\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"itk1665703199671__p_d136070e1_d136071e1_d136072e1\">The value returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span> is\n            always <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"itk1665703199671__section_zzc_sjg_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d450261e95\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"itk1665703199671__p_d135212e1_d135213e1_d135214e1\">Allowed in all Uniface component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"itk1665703199671__section_d3n_tjg_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d450261e104\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"itk1665703199671__p_d136043e1_d136044e1_d136045e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">getMessage()</span> operation gets\n            the message from the current instance of the UTIMER component for the given destination\n            component instance.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528701\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528701\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "getMessage() Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 25, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Get the timer message from the UTIMER component. Explain this code operation getMessage params string MsgDestination : OUT string MsgId : OUT string MsgData : OUT endparams Copy Parameters MsgDestination —path to the component instance to which the message is sent. MsgId —message ID of the message that is sent to the component. MsgData —message data that is sent to the component. Return Values The value returned in $status is always 0 . Use Allowed in all Uniface component types. Description The getMessage() operation gets the message from the current instance of the UTIMER component for the given destination component instance. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}